item_category: The Fury is powered by an Intel i5-10400F. With an optimal balance of frequency, cores and threads, optional advanced tuning support, and blazing connectivity, this 10th Gen Intel Core processor supercharges the system for competitive and premium performance. Combined with an RTX 3070 Graphics Card, the Fierce Fury delivers amazing graphics and performance. Windows 10 Home is pre-installed on this system, allowing you to plug and play right out of the box.
